---
// VLSI Korea Changelog Banner (static)
---

<div class='border-t bg-white py-6 text-left sm:py-16 sm:text-center'>
  <div class='container max-w-[650px]!'>
    <p class='text-2xl font-bold sm:text-5xl'>
      <img
        src='/img/gifs/rocket.gif'
        alt='Rocket'
        class='mr-2 hidden h-12 w-12 sm:inline'
      />
      Semiconductor Career Roadmaps
    </p>
    <p
      class='mt-1 mb-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 sm:my-5 sm:text-lg'
    >
      Curated by VLSI Korea. Built on 15+ years of semiconductor design experience.
      Updated regularly with new learning resources.
    </p>

    <div class='relative mt-2 text-left sm:mt-8'>
      <div
        class='absolute inset-y-0 left-[120px] hidden w-px translate-x-[5.75px] bg-gray-300 sm:block'
      >
      </div>

      <div class='ml-[35px] flex items-start gap-2 sm:ml-0'>
        <div class='relative mr-2 hidden h-3 w-3 shrink-0 sm:block'>
          <div class='absolute inset-0 z-10 rounded-full bg-blue-500'></div>
          <div class='absolute -inset-1 z-0 animate-ping rounded-full bg-blue-200'></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400'>2025-06-07</p>
          <p class='text-lg font-medium'>Initial Release</p>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-600'>
            7 tracks live: STA, Physical Design, RTL Design, Design Verification, Analog Design, DFT, EDA Toolflow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
